data.description: Beautifully Renovated Throughout ! 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Ranch on Cul-de-sac Lot. New Paint Inside and Out. New Flooring, Lighting and Fixtures Throughout. Vault Ceiling Family Room w/Fireplace. Kitchen w/New Granite Countertops, New Solid Surface Oven Range, New Dishwasher. Dining Area. Spacious Master w/Trey Ceiling And Walk-In Closet. Master Bath w/New Double Vanity, Garden Tub and Step-In Shower. 2 Additional Bedrooms Share A Hall Bath w/New Vanity. New Architectural Shingle Roof, New Water Heater. Quiet Subdivision Minutes From Downtown Senoia.
